SMHUP Patterns by Donald E. Llopis 2011 (machinezilla@gmail.com)

A demonstration of how to create Galaga style formation movement
patterns using pattern tables and analytic geometry.

Developed using: html canvas and javascript.

For a detailed explaination of the techniques used please see this
blog post:

http://www.machinezilla.com/2011/08/galaga-dual-formations-explained.html


